                <mxCell id="30" value="Why wxO is not just a connector:&#10;- Semantic routing — parses JSON, decides which tools to call&#10;- Conversational Q&amp;A — ad-hoc governance questions in plain English&#10;- Cross-repo fan-out — one agent serves every repo&#10;- Fallback logic — detects OpenPages failure, re-routes email&#10;- Future: escalation, team routing, dedup logic" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1310" width="370" height="110" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="31" value="Payload field mapping (aidlc-governance-event/v1 to OpenPages):&#10;- violations[].rule   to   Control ID / Issue Type&#10;- violations[].detail   to   Issue Description&#10;- violations[].severity   to   Risk Rating (critical/high/medium)&#10;- actor   to   Reported By&#10;- pr_url   to   Evidence URL&#10;- repo + project   to   Business Entity&#10;- timestamp   to   Created Date&#10;- verdict=FAIL   to   Status = Open&#10;- verdict=PASS   to   Status = Closed (auto)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fffacd;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="440" y="1310" width="360" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="32" value="OpenPages owns email in production:&#10;- Audited in GRC audit log (CIP-010 traceable)&#10;- Throttled via IMR bulletin scheduling&#10;- Retried automatically on mail server failure&#10;- Template owned by compliance team&#10;- No extra Azure credentials needed in wxO" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#107C10;fontColor=#0a3d0a;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="830" y="1380" width="270" height="110" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="33" value="Migration path (when ready):&#10;1. Create OpenPages schema + custom fields&#10;2. Configure WF Engine email template (Open stage)&#10;3. Deploy agent — verify OpenPages email arrives&#10;4. Remove send_outlook_email from tools list&#10;5. Remove OUTLOOK_* secrets and redeploy" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff3cd;strokeColor=#f0a30a;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1440" width="370" height="110" as="geometry"/>
